because...

546
00:36:58,823 --> 00:37:00,154
I...

547
00:37:05,230 --> 00:37:09,064
Because she wanted to have
her little teddy all to herself,

548
00:37:09,134 --> 00:37:11,466
and since then,
he's been a queer and a crook.

549
00:37:11,537 --> 00:37:13,096
You see?

550
00:37:15,108 --> 00:37:17,201
You're an asshole!

551
