Oh! Sorry.

563
00:37:50,247 --> 00:37:52,113
Of course.
What answer would you like?

564
00:37:53,017 --> 00:37:54,848
What would satisfy you?

565
00:37:57,188 --> 00:38:00,454
Anyway, what I said isn't true.
You know that as well as I.

566
00:38:02,294 --> 00:38:03,955
Look at him.

567
00:38:04,697 --> 00:38:07,667
Do you really think he comes from
a deprived background?

568
00:38:08,401 --> 00:38:09,834
