578
00:38:50,849 --> 00:38:53,011
I'll see what there is.

579
00:38:59,960 --> 00:39:02,554
You see, the truth is,
he's a drug addict.

580
00:39:03,897 --> 00:39:06,229
That's why he's going now, and...

581
